lead_paragraph: Brandon Phillips had a sacrifice fly and Adam Duvall added a two-run single in the first inning off Danny Salazar, leading the Cincinnati Reds to a 9-1 win over the Cleveland Indians.

headline.print_headline: Reds' Phillips, Duvall Hurt Salazar in 9-1 Win vs Indians
